steps.step: {"blocks":[{"key":"fvb64","text":"The mouse is immobilized in a self-made restraint tube. ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"86cd2","text":"Apply 10% povidone–iodine solution to the plantar surface of bilateral hind paws with a cotton bud. Once dry, coat the skin surface with a suspension of 100% starch–castor oil.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"nokq","text":"Sweat droplets are visualized as dark-colored spots because of iodine–starch reactions. Changes on footpads are video-recorded for 3 min. The number of dark spots was counted for each paw.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"3kmoa","text":"The mouse is placed in the supine position under sevoflurane anesthesia (4 volume% in 1 L/min oxygen) . ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"15osf","text":"Apply 10% povidone–iodine solution to the plantar surface of bilateral hind paws with a cotton bud. Once dry, coat the skin surface with a suspension of 100% starch–castor oil.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"c3rkv","text":"Inject 100 µg pilocarpine hydrochloride (diluted in 150 µL 0.9% saline) intraperitoneally.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"43rn7","text":"Sweat droplets are visualized as dark-colored spots because of iodine–starch reactions. Changes on footpads are video-recorded for 5 min. The number of dark spots was counted for each paw.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
